@startuml 4B_Order_Lifecycle
title 4-B · Order Placement & Lifecycle (UC-F30 to UC-F42, UC-T30 to UC-T32, UC-S05 to UC-S09)

start
|Registered Fan|
:Browse merch products;
:View product details and variants;
:Add selected variant to cart;
:Update or remove cart items if needed;
:Click Checkout;

|System|
:Verify fan is logged in;
if (Fan authenticated?) then (No)
  :Redirect to Login;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Validate cart, stock and delivery address;
endif

if (Cart valid and stock available?) then (No)
  :Return out_of_stock / address error;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Create MerchOrder status = PENDING;
  :Snapshot cart items into order items;
  :Reserve stock and clear cart;
endif

|Registered Fan|
:Select payment method\n(Credit Card / PayPal / Stripe / QR Bank Transfer);

|System|
:Create Payment status = PENDING;
if (Payment method is QR Bank Transfer?) then (Yes)
  :Generate QR code and expiry time;
  |Registered Fan|
  :Scan QR and complete bank transfer;
else (No)
  :Redirect or initialize provider payment flow;
endif

|Payment Gateway|
:Send payment webhook callback;

|System|
:Verify webhook signature;
if (Webhook/payment valid?) then (No)
  :Mark payment FAILED or keep order PENDING;
  :Log failure / invalid signature;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Set Payment status = COMPLETED;
  :Transition order PENDING -> PAID;
  :Create Shipment status = PREPARING;
  :Notify fan and Tenant Admin;
endif

|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
:View paid orders;
:Enter carrier, tracking number and ETA;

|System|
:Transition order PAID -> SHIPPED;
:Notify fan shipment update;

|Registered Fan|
if (Fan action?) then (Track Order)
  |System|
  :Return latest shipment status;
elseif (Fan action?) then (Cancel Pending Order)
  |System|
  :Cancel only if order policy allows;
else (Return Request)
  |Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
  :Review return request;
  |System|
  :Record return processing result;
endif

stop
@enduml
